|2 |│ └─EXCHANGE OUT DISTR   |:EX10000|8       |20          |
|3 |│   └─PX BLOCK ITERATOR  |        |8       |17          |
|4 |│     └─TABLE FULL SCAN  |t_audit |8       |17          |
